nmap + zI
nmap - zO
nmap 0 zz
nmap <C-j> 5j
nmap <C-k> 5k
nnoremap b :open !
nnoremap B :tabopen !
nnoremap <C-y> Y

shortcut-default goo
shortcut-add goo=https://www.google.com/search?q=$0
